				<p>ExpressionEngine 3.5.7 is now available for download.</p>

<p>I know some folks who will be very happy to see improvements to channel navigation when editing a channel that is limited to 1 entry.  Click on the channel name under &#8216;Edit&#8217; and you&#8217;ll go directly to the entry.  And Grid fields now respect assigned column widths, another popular request.</p>

<p>We&#8217;ve made optimizations to the File Manager, template parsing, and the RSS module, and fixed some frontend member profile pop-ups, where the private message and email pop-ups didn‚Äôt show correctly.</p>

<p>Channel forms also got a tweak to prevent clashing javascript when more than one form is on the page and there were fixes for comments, member notification settings, and category edits from the publish page.</p>

<p>Visit the <a href="https://docs.expressionengine.com/v3/about/changelog.html#version-3-5-7">changelog</a> to view all of the changes.</p>

